## API Documentation Summary
- **Main Endpoint**: `https://apifreellm.com/api/v1/chat`
- **Compatibility**:
  - **Free Tier**: Custom format (NOT OpenAI compatible).
  - **Premium Tier ($12/month)**: OpenAI-compatible (drop-in replacement).
- **Request Body (Free Tier - Custom)**:
  ```json
  {
    "message": "Your prompt here",
    "model": "apifreellm" (optional)
  }
  ```
- **Headers**:
  ```
  Content-Type: application/json
  Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY
  ```
- **Response Example**:
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "response": "AI generated text...",
    "tier": "free",
    "features": { ... }
  }
  ```
- **Limitations (Free Tier)**: 1 request every 25 seconds, 32k context.

